#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is a stopwatch application. It can be used for basic tasks like "
"timer start/pause/resume, as well as lap times recording."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; je aplikacija za štoparico. Uporablja se lahko za osnovna "
"opravila, kot je zagon/premor/nadaljevanje z merilnikom časa, pa tudi za "
"beleženje časov krogov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is able to save a complete session (timer and lap times) and to "
"restore it later."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; lahko shrani celotno sejo (merilnik časa in čas kroga) in jo "
"pozneje obnovi."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kronometer"
msgstr "Kronometer"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "stopwatch"
msgstr "štoparica"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is a simple stopwatch application. It is meant to be simple and "
"pleasant to use, thanks to a use cases driven development."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; je preprosta aplikacija za štoparico. Zahvaljujoč razvoju, ki "
"temelji na primerih uporabe, naj bi bil preprost in prijeten za uporabo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; main features are the following:"
msgstr "&kronometer; glavne značilnosti so naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; provides a timer that can be started, paused, resumed and reset."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; ponuja merilnik časa, ki ga je mogoče zagnati, začasno "
"ustaviti, nadaljevati in ponastaviti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; allows you to record lap times and export them to a file."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; omogoča beleženje časov krogov in njihov izvoz v datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; allows you to save a session and restore it later."
msgstr "&kronometer; vam omogoča, da shranite sejo in jo pozneje obnovite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; allows you to copy the timer numbers from its display."
msgstr "&kronometer; omogoča kopiranje številk časovnika z njegovega zaslona."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Uporaba"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Usage"
msgstr "Splošna uporaba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; main use case is of course the interaction with the timer. You "
"can start/pause/resume the timer by clicking on the proper actions in the "
"toolbar or in the &kronometer; menu."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; glavni primer uporabe je seveda interakcija z merilnikom časa. "
"Merilnik časa lahko zaženete/začasno ustavite/nadaljujete s klikom na "
"ustrezna dejanja v orodni vrstici ali v meniju &kronometer;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Even simpler, you can use the keyboard instead of the mouse: you start the "
"timer with the keyboard's <keycap>Space</keycap> and you pause the timer "
"with <keycap>Space</keycap> too. You might recognize this behavior from many "
"media player applications."
msgstr ""
"Še preprosteje, namesto miške lahko uporabite tipkovnico: merilnik časa "
"zaženete s tipko <keycap>preslednica</keycap> na tipkovnici in prekinete "
"časovnik tudi s <keycap>preslednico</keycap>. To vedenje boste morda "
"prepoznali v številnih aplikacijah predvajalnika medijev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By pressing the &Enter; key when the timer is running, you freeze that "
"particular time and you create a new <emphasis>lap</emphasis> time. These "
"times are always visible in the table on the left of the application, where "
"you can sort them by clicking the <emphasis>Lap time</emphasis> column's "
"header. You can also add a custom text annotation to each lap, by double-"
"clicking the cells within the <emphasis>Note</emphasis> column."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom na &Enter; ko merilnik časa teče, zamrznete ta čas in ustvarite "
"nov čas <emphasis>kroga</emphasis>. Ti časi so vedno vidni v tabeli na levi "
"strani aplikacije, kjer jih lahko razvrstite tako, da kliknete glavo stolpca "
"<emphasis>Čas kroga</emphasis>. Vsakemu krogu lahko dodate tudi besedilno "
"opombo po meri, tako da dvokliknete celice v stolpcu <emphasis>Opomba</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menubar (hidden by default) provides access to all commands and "
"configuration options. The menubar can be toggled with <guimenuitem>Show "
"Menubar</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></"
"keycombo>) from the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu or the menu button in "
"the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Menijska vrstica (privzeto skrita) omogoča dostop do vseh ukazov in "
"konfiguracijskih možnosti. Menijsko vrstico lahko preklopite s "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži menijsko vrstico</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>) v meniju <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> ali menijski gumb v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save and Restore Sessions"
msgstr "Shrani in obnovi seje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you pause a running stopwatch you create a session: a stopwatch time "
"and zero or more lap times. You can save a session and you can restore it "
"later."
msgstr ""
"Ko začasno ustavite tekočo štoparico, ustvarite sejo: čas štoparice in nič "
"ali več časov kroga. Sejo lahko shranite in jo pozneje obnovite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save a Session"
msgstr "Shrani sejo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pause a running stopwatch, then click on the <guibutton>Save As</guibutton> "
"button in the <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. You can choose a name for the "
"session that you are going to save."
msgstr ""
"Zaustavite delujočo štoparico, nato kliknite gumb <guibutton>Shrani kot</"
"guibutton> v meniju <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>. Izberete lahko ime za sejo, "
"ki jo boste shranili."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restore a Session"
msgstr "Obnovi sejo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Open</guibutton> button on the toolbar or in the "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. Then choose an existing session to be loaded "
"from the session's dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <guibutton>Odpri</guibutton> v orodni vrstici ali v meniju "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>. Nato v pogovornem oknu seje izberite obstoječo "
"sejo, ki jo želite naložiti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Update a Session"
msgstr "Posodobite sejo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the session is restored, you can resume the stopwatch and you can "
"record new lap times. If you want to save the updated session, you can "
"simply click the <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button in the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Ko je seja obnovljena, lahko nadaljujete s štoparico in beležite nove čase "
"krogov. Če želite shraniti posodobljeno sejo, lahko preprosto kliknete gumb "
"<guibutton>Shrani</guibutton> v meniju <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit a Session"
msgstr "Urejanje seje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Open</guibutton> button on the toolbar or in the "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. If you select an existing session in the "
"session's dialog, you will be able to:"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <guibutton>Odpri</guibutton> v orodni vrstici ali v meniju "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>. Če izberete obstoječo sejo v pogovornem oknu "
"seje, boste lahko:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename the session, by double-clicking on its name."
msgstr "Preimenujte sejo tako, da dvokliknete njeno ime."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete the session, by pressing <keycap>Del</keycap>."
msgstr "Izbrišite sejo s pritiskom <keycap>Del</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add a note to the session or edit it."
msgstr "Seji dodajte opombo ali jo uredite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional Features"
msgstr "Dodatne lastnosti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export Lap Times"
msgstr "Izvozi čase krogov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you record one or more lap times, the export features in the "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu is made available, under the entry "
"<guimenuitem>Export laps as</guimenuitem>. Click on it and then choose a "
"name for the exported file. You can export in the Comma Separated Values "
"(CSV) format or in the JSON one."
msgstr ""
"Ko zabeležite enega ali več časov krogov, so na voljo izvozne funkcije v "
"meniju <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> pod vnosom <guimenuitem>Izvozi kroge kot</"
"guimenuitem>. Kliknite nanjo in nato izberite ime za izvoženo datoteko. "
"Izvozite lahko v formatu vrednosti, ločenih z vejico (CSV) ali v formatu "
"JSON."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clipboard Support"
msgstr "Podpora za odložišče"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is able to copy the current stopwatch time to the system "
"clipboard. Use the <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> key "
"combination or the <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> entry in the "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; lahko kopira trenutni čas štoparice v sistemsko odložišče. "
"Uporabite kombinacijo tipk <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> ali "
"vnos <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is customizable in many aspects. You can open the settings "
"dialog clicking on the <guimenuitem>Configure &kronometer;</guimenuitem> "
"entry in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu. The settings dialog is "
"organized in the following categories."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; je prilagodljiv v mnogih pogledih. Pogovorno okno z "
"nastavitvami lahko odprete s klikom na vnos <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kronometer;</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu>. Pogovorno "
"okno z nastavitvami je organizirano v naslednjih kategorijah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "Splošne nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the general settings page you can find the settings for the stopwatch and "
"for the laps. Under the stopwatch tab you can set your preferred time format "
"for the stopwatch display. You can choose whether to show hours, minutes or "
"second fractions (while seconds are always shown). &kronometer; supports "
"time granularity up to millisecond, although this requires high CPU usage "
"due to the high refresh rate of the User Interface."
msgstr ""
"Na strani s splošnimi nastavitvami najdete nastavitve za štoparico in kroge. "
"Pod zavihkom štoparica lahko nastavite želeno obliko časa za prikaz "
"štoparice. Izberete lahko, ali želite prikazati ure, minute ali delčke "
"sekund (sekunde pa so vedno prikazane). &kronometer; podpira razdrobljenost "
"časa do milisekunde, čeprav to zahteva veliko porabo procesorja zaradi "
"visoke stopnje osveževanja uporabniškega vmesnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Within the laps tab you can enable or disable the laps recording feature. If "
"the laps are enabled, you can choose their time format, whether to show "
"their notes and whether to show their absolute times, which are the "
"stopwatch times when they were recorded."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku krogi lahko omogočite ali onemogočite funkcijo beleženja krogov. "
"Če so krogi omogočeni, lahko izberete njihovo obliko časa, ali želite "
"prikazati njihove opombe in ali želite prikazati njihove absolutne čase, ki "
"so časi štoparice, ko so bili zabeleženi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve pisave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the font settings page you can customize the font of the stopwatch "
"display. You can choose different font families, styles and sizes for each "
"timer component (hours, minutes, &etc;). By default every timer component "
"will use the same font, according the current default font in the system."
msgstr ""
"Na strani z nastavitvami pisave lahko prilagodite pisavo prikaza štoparice. "
"Izberete lahko različne družine pisav, sloge in velikosti za vsako "
"komponento časovnika (ure, minute &etc;). Privzeto bo vsaka komponenta "
"časovnika uporabljala isto pisavo glede na trenutno privzeto pisavo v "
"sistemu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Settings"
msgstr "Barvne nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the color settings page you can customize the default color of the "
"stopwatch display. You can change the background color and the text color. "
"The default colors will respect the currently selected system's theme."
msgstr ""
"Na strani z nastavitvami barv lahko prilagodite privzeto barvo prikaza "
"štoparice. Spremenite lahko barvo ozadja in barvo besedila. Privzete barve "
"bodo upoštevale trenutno izbrano temo sistema."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Built-in Settings"
msgstr "&kde; Vgrajene nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; makes use of the standard &kde; configuration tools. You find "
"them in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu, under the "
"<guimenuitem>Configure shortcuts</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Toolbars</guimenuitem> entries. They allow you to change the shortcuts of "
"the &kronometer;'s actions, and to change the position of the toolbar and "
"its content."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; uporablja standard &kde; konfiguracijska orodja. Najdete jih v "
"meniju <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> pod vnosoma <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"bližnjice</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj orodne vrstice</"
"guimenuitem>. Omogočajo vam spreminjanje bližnjic do dejanj &kronometer; ter "
"spreminjanje položaja orodne vrstice in njene vsebine."

